songs.title: Who is Bestita
songs.lyrics:
Who is this Saboki?
Who is Bestita?
Ok

These two subjects are the same people
Personalities of the same
The two complement each other

The mix of these individuals is the result of
SADBOYTAKI

Two very similar personalities
But at the same time very odd

But these can be fractioned thus forming
To more examples, these are the result of sadboytaki
But these can be fractioned thus forming
To more examples, these are the result of sadboytaki
